### ============================================
### 4.3 ROADMAP & HOME ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### GET /v1/roadmap?groupId=...
### Obtener roadmap del grupo con progreso
GET {{baseUrl}}/roadmap?groupId={{groupId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================

### GET /v1/home
### Dashboard principal con roadmap y métricas
GET {{baseUrl}}/home
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### ERROR CASES
### ============================================

### GET /v1/roadmap - Missing groupId
GET {{baseUrl}}/roadmap
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================

### GET /v1/roadmap - Invalid groupId
GET {{baseUrl}}/roadmap?groupId=invalid-uuid
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================

### GET /v1/home - User not completed onboarding
GET {{baseUrl}}/home
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
